sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 사용자
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant UC as RunAgentUseCase
    participant Policy as Policy Guard
    participant Planner as Retrieval Planner
    participant Vector as Vector Search
    participant Synth as Answer Synthesizer
    participant Audit as Audit Log

    User->>API: POST /v1/agents/runs
    API->>UC: execute(message, scenario)
    UC->>Policy: redact(message)
    Policy-->>UC: redacted_query, redaction_count
    UC->>Planner: classify + plan
    Planner-->>UC: query_type, strategy
    UC->>Policy: evaluate(query_type)
    alt approval required
        UC->>Audit: agent.answer.generated(blocked)
        UC-->>API: blocked response
    else allowed
        UC->>Vector: search(query, top_k)
        Vector-->>UC: chunks + scores
        UC->>Synth: synthesize grounded answer
        Synth-->>UC: answer + citations
        UC->>Audit: agent.answer.generated(succeeded)
        UC-->>API: answer + citations + trace
    end
